race.comment: MISSISSIPPI DREAM (7) will be ready to peak now fourth run back and must be respected from the Vandyke barn. Maloney on board and shapes as one of the leading hopes. SEXY TIME (3) was well in the betting when facing the starter for the first time and where there's smoke there's fire. Can feature prominently from the favourable draw. RATENOTICE (12) may have suffered from the dreaded second-up syndrome at the latest outing but the three runs prior were good enough for this. Can bounce right back without surprising. AMAZARA (5) just missed the frame on debut and rounds out the selections in a competitive affair.
